        public Transaction(ClientType clientType,
                   java.lang.String clientDetails,
                   ActionType actionType,
                   ComponentType componentType,
                   java.lang.String componentDetails,
                   boolean success,
                   java.lang.String exception)
        Main constractor for Transaction.
        Parameters:
        clientType - Enum of the client type who did the action in the system. (Admin, Company, Customer)
        clientDetails - The client Details who did the action in the system.
        actionType - Enum of the action the client did in the system. (Login, Create, Update, Remove, Purchase)
        componentType - Enum of the component type that the client did the action on. (Admin, Company, Customer, Coupon)
        componentDetails - the Component Details that the client did the action on.
        success - Did the action succeed or not.
        exception - The exception that made the action to fail.
